\'93Ay, ay,\'94 said Slightly at once, and disappeared, scratching his head. But he knew Peter must be obeyed, and he returned in a moment, wearing John\'92s hat and looking solemn.\
\'93Please, sir,\'94 said Peter, going to him, \'93are you a doctor?\'94\
