\'93No, no,\'94 he told Wendy decisively; \'93perhaps she would say I was old, and I just want always to be a little boy and to have fun.\'94\
\'93But, Peter\'97\'94\
\'93No.\'94\
And so the others had to be told.\
\'93Peter isn\'92t coming.\'94\
